title: Jed York on substation injury theory: "I think we can debunk it"

sources.name: Yahoo Sports NFL
sources.title: Jed York on substation injury theory: "I think we can debunk it"
sources.description: The 49ers have a perception problem when it comes to the possibility that their uptick in injuries has been caused by the proximity of the team's practice facility to an electrical substation.
